import { Box, Stack, Text } from '@chakra-ui/react'

function App() {
  return (
    <Box h="100%">
      <Stack spacing={0} direction='column'>
        <Stack spacing={0} direction='row'>
          <Box w="100%" h="100%">
            <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#81ecec' color='white'> #81ecec </Text>
          </Box>
          <Box w="100%" h="100%">
            <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#74b9ff' color='white'> #74b9ff </Text>
          </Box>
          <Box w="100%" h="100%">
            <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#a29bfe' color='white'> #a29bfe </Text>
          </Box>
        </Stack>
        <Stack spacing={0} direction='row'>
        <Box w="100%" h="100%">
          <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#00cec9' color='white'> #00cec9 </Text>
        </Box>
        <Box w="100%" h="100%">
         <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#0984e3' color='white'> #0984e3 </Text>
        </Box>
        <Box w="100%" h="100%">
          <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#6c5ce7' color='white'> #6c5ce7 </Text>
        </Box>
          
        </Stack>
        <Stack spacing={0} direction='row'>
          <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#fab1a0' color='white'>#fab1a0 </Text>
          <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#ff7675' color='white'> #ff7675</Text>
          <Text fontWeight='bold' fontSize='large' backgroundColor='#fd79a8' color='white'> #fd79a8 </Text>
        </Stack>
        
      </Stack>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default App;
